<SYNC Start=1211835><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1212878><P Class=ENCC>
You know what,<br>I'm gonna make this up to you.
<SYNC Start=1215642><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1215847><P Class=ENCC>
I promised you a stripper..
<SYNC Start=1217542><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1219451><P Class=ENCC>
and you're gonna get a stripper.
<SYNC Start=1222011><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
