<SYNC Start=1226421><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1227292><P Class=ENCC>
Carry on.
<SYNC Start=1229351><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1245110><P Class=ENCC>
These tennis shoes are so tight.
<SYNC Start=1249137><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1250249><P Class=ENCC>
-I think I'll take them off.<br>-Could you not narrate?
<SYNC Start=1254208><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1255887><P Class=ENCC>
Gotcha, sailor.
<SYNC Start=1257946><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1266031><P Class=ENCC>
Just because<br>you're not in love with the guy..
<SYNC Start=1268932><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
