<SYNC Start=1278804><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1281146><P Class=ENCC>
Bye, Dad.
<SYNC Start=1283444><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1288153><P Class=ENCC>
It's unacceptable! What the hell does love<br>have to do with it?
<SYNC Start=1291782><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1292024><P Class=ENCC>
