<SYNC Start=1303598><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1305671><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, I do think about<br>the consequences of my decisions!
<SYNC Start=1310335><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1311243><P Class=ENCC>
Well, what gives you the right to..?
<SYNC Start=1313711><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1313912><P Class=ENCC>
Go to hell!
<SYNC Start=1316210><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
